Nature had come into her own again,and littla by little

14
00:02:29,102 --> 00:02:32,542
渐渐把她细长的手指顽强而偷偷摸摸地

15
00:02:30,651 --> 00:02:35,065
had encroached upon the drive with long,tenacious fingers.

16
00:02:32,647 --> 00:02:35,774
