再见  迈克斯  一起走吧  丹尼
Toodle-oo,Max. Come along,Danny.

1936
02:00:17,378 --> 02:00:21,340
别打扰这对不幸福的夫妇一起度过最后的时光了
Let’s leave the unhappy couple to speed their last moments together alone.

1937
02:00:32,184 --> 02:00:34,478
你确定不要我跟你一起去吗  迈克西姆
Are you sure you don’t want me to go with you,Max?

1938
02:00:34,478 --> 02:00:36,564
是的  亲爱的  那会使你疲惫不堪的
No,darling. It’ll be very tiring for you.

1939
02:00:36,772 --> 02:00:39,077
我一大早就会回去了
I’ll be back the very first thing in the morning.

1940
02:00:39,077 --> 02:00:40,526
我会不眠不休地赶回去
-And I won’t even stop to sleep. -I’ll be waiting for you.

1941
02:00:40,526 --> 02:00:42,716
我等你

1942
02:00:48,242 --> 02:00:50,849
-好了吗  迈克西姆  -好了
-Ready,Maxim? -Yes.

1943
02:00:50,849 --> 02:00:53,768
你们俩开前面  我跟着费弗尔
You two go on ahead. I'll follow with Favell.

1944
02:01:07,324 --> 02:01:08,429
贝克医生
COLONEL JULYAN:Dr.Baker,you may have seen

1945
02:01:08,429 --> 02:01:11,911
最近你也许在报纸上看过德温特先生的名字
Mr.de Winter’s name in the pepers renently.

1946
02:01:11,911 --> 02:01:15,770
是的 跟一具在船上被发现的尸体有关
Yes. Yes. In connection with the body that was found in a boat.

1947
02:01:15,770 --> 02:01:18,689
我太太看了所有报道  令人伤心的案件
My wife was reading all about it. A very sad case. My condolences.

1948
02:01:18,689 --> 02:01:21,192
-同情   -这将花去数小时  容我
FAVELL: This is going to take hours. Let me...

1949
02:01:21,192 --> 02:01:24,111
别费心了  费弗尔  我想我可以告诉贝克医生
Don’t bother,Favell. I think I can tell Dr.Baker.

1950
02:01:24,111 --> 02:01:26,509
我们想要了解某些有关
We’re trying to discover certain facts

1951
02:01:26,509 --> 02:01:29,950
前任德温特太太去世当天的活动真相
concerning the late Mrs.de Winter’s activities on the day of her death.

1952
02:01:29,950 --> 02:01:33,496
去年  10月12号  如果你记得的话  我想你告诉我
October the 12th,last year

1953
02:01:31,785 --> 02:01:33,446
I want you to tell me if you can,

1954
02:01:33,496 --> 02:01:36,832
那天是否有叫这个名字的人拜访过你
if anyone of that name paid you a visit on that date?

1955
02:01:36,832 --> 02:01:39,960
非常抱歉  恐怕我帮不上忙
I’m awfully sorry. I’m afraid I can't help you.

1956
02:01:40,065 --> 02:01:42,567
我是记得有个叫德温特的人
I should have remembered the name de Winter.

1957
02:01:42,567 --> 02:01:45,174
但我从未给一个叫德温特太太的人看过病
I’ve never attended a Mrs.de Winter in my life.

1958
02:01:45,174 --> 02:01:48,093
你怎么可能记得所有你病人的名字
FAVELL: How can you possibly tell all your patients'names?

1959
02:01:48,093 --> 02:01:51,534
如果你想的话  我可以从预约本上找找
I can look it up is my engagement diary if you like.

1960
02:01:51,534 --> 02:01:54,663
-你是说10月12号吗  -是的
-Did you say the 12th of October? -COLONEL JULYAN:Yes.

1961
02:01:54,663 --> 02:01:59,459
找到了  没有  没有叫德温特的
Here we era.

1962
02:01:56,810 --> 02:01:58,675
No. No de Winter

1963
02:01:59,459 --> 02:02:03,317
-你确定吗  -这是那天所有的预约
Are you sure?

1964
02:02:01,022 --> 02:02:03,559
Well,here are all the appointments for that day.

1965
02:02:03,317 --> 02:02:06,862
"罗丝  坎贝尔  斯蒂尔  佩里诺  丹弗斯  马修 "
Ross,Campbell Steadall,Perrino Danvers...

1966
02:02:06,862 --> 02:02:09,365
丹尼  见鬼
-Danny? What the devil? -Would you read that name again?

1967
02:02:09,365 --> 02:02:12,806
可以再念一遍名字吗  你念到丹弗斯?

1968
02:02:10,990 --> 02:02:12,776
Did you say Danvers?

1969
02:02:12,806 --> 02:02:15,517
是的  3点有位丹弗斯太太的预约
Yes. I have a Mrs.Danvers for 3:00.

1970
02:02:15,517 --> 02:02:17,915
她长什么样  你还记得吗
What did she look like? Can you remember?

1971
02:02:17,915 --> 02:02:21,252
记得  我记得很清楚  她是位非常漂亮的女人
Yes,I remember her quite well. She was e very beautiful woman.

1972
02:02:21,252 --> 02:02:24,276
高挑个儿  黑黑的脸蛋  穿着很精致
-Tall dark,exquisitely dressed. -CRAWLEY: Rebecca.

1973
02:02:24,276 --> 02:02:27,612
-是丽贝卡  -那位女士肯定用了化名
The lady must have used an assumed name.

1974
02:02:27,612 --> 02:02:33,451
是吗  真是令人吃惊  我认识她很久了
Is that so?

1975
02:02:30,009 --> 02:02:33,001
This is a surprise. I’ve known her a long time.

1976
02:02:33,451 --> 02:02:35,015
她得了什么病
What was the matter with her?

1977
02:02:35,120 --> 02:02:37,205
尊敬的先生  我们有职业操守
Well,there are certain ethics.

1978
02:02:37,205 --> 02:02:41,167
你可能提供德温特太太自杀的原因  贝克医生
Could you supply a reason Dr.Baker,for Mrs. de Winter’s suicide?

1979
02:02:41,167 --> 02:02:44,191
是谋杀  她怀孕了  不是吗
For her murder,you mean?

1980
02:02:42,230 --> 02:02:45,438
She wan going to have a kid,wasn't she? Come on. Out with it!

1981
02:02:44,191 --> 02:02:46,172
快点  快说
Tell me,what else would a woman of her class be doing in a dump like this?

1982
02:02:46,172 --> 02:02:49,301
她这种高尚的女人怎么会做这样污秽的事

1983
02:02:49,301 --> 02:02:50,583
我以警方的名义来访  对我来说有必要
I take it the official nature of this visit makes it necessary for me to...

1984
02:02:50,583 --> 02:02:52,220
使你相信如果没必要的话
I assure you we’d not be troubling you if it were not necessary.

1985
02:02:52,220 --> 02:02:56,391
我们就不会来打扰你了

1986
02:02:56,391 --> 02:02:58,893
你们想知道我是否可以指出任何有关
You want to know if I can suggest any motive

1987
02:02:58,893 --> 02:03:01,605
德温特太太会自杀的动机?
as to why Mrs.de Winter should have taken her life?

1988
02:03:01,605 --> 02:03:04,837
我想可以
Yes,I think I can.

1989
02:03:06,505 --> 02:03:10,363
那位自称丹弗斯太太的女人得了很严重的病
The woman who called herself Mrs.Danvers was very seriously ill.

1990
02:03:10,363 --> 02:03:13,908
我不是怀孕了吗
She was not going to have a child?

1991
02:03:13,908 --> 02:03:17,766
她以为是  但我的诊断却不同
That was what she thought. My diagnosis was different.

1992
02:03:17,766 --> 02:03:22,980
我让她去找一位知名的专科医生做检查  照X光
I sent her to a well-known specialist for an axamination and x-rays.

1993
02:03:22,980 --> 02:03:26,942
而那天她是拿她的检查报告来给我看的
And on this date,she returned to me for his report.

1994
02:03:26,942 --> 02:03:31,009
我记得她站在这儿拿着她的X光片
I rememder her standing here holding out her hand for the photograph.

1995
02:03:31,009 --> 02:03:33,199
她说  "我想知道真相"
“I want to know the truth,”she said.

1996
02:03:33,199 --> 02:03:36,222
"我不要听冠冕堂皇的话"
“I don't want soft words and a bedside manner.

1997
02:03:36,222 --> 02:03:39,038
"如果有病  你可以马上告诉我"
If I’m for it you can tell me right away.”

1998
02:03:39,038 --> 02:03:41,645
我知道她不是那种听了假话会信以为真的人
I knew she was not the tyge to accept a lie.

1999
02:03:41,645 --> 02:03:44,564
她要听实话  所有我就告诉她了
She’d asked for the truth,so I let her have it.

2000
02:03:44,564 --> 02:03:48,631
她跟我道谢之后  我再也没有见过她了  所有我猜想
She thanked me. I never saw her again,so I assumed...

2001
02:03:48,631 --> 02:03:51,759
-她得了什么病  -癌症
-What was wrong with her? -Cancer.

2002
02:03:54,261 --> 02:03:56,764
是的  癌症晚期
Yes,the growth was deep-rooted.

2003
02:03:56,764 --> 02:03:59,788
动手术也完全无济于事
An operation would have been no earthly use at all.

2004
02:03:59,788 --> 02:04:02,499
要不了多久  她就得靠吗啡来止痛了
In a short time,she would have been under morphia.

2005
02:04:02,499 --> 02:04:06,044
除了等死  没什么可做的了
There was nothing that could be done for her,except wait.

2006
02:04:06,148 --> 02:04:09,902
当你告诉她病情的时候  她有说什么吗
MAXIM:Did she say anything when you told her?

2007
02:04:09,902 --> 02:04:13,343
她怪异地微笑着
DR.BAKER:She smiled in a queer sort of way.

2008
02:04:13,343 --> 02:04:16,262
你的妻子是个很棒的女人  德温特先生
Your wife was a wonderful woman,Mr.de Winter.

2009
02:04:16,262 --> 02:04:19,078
对了  我记得她说了一些
And,oh,yes,I remember she said something

2010
02:04:19,182 --> 02:04:22,102
当时令我觉得非常奇怪的话
that struck me as being very peculiar at the time.

2011
02:04:22,102 --> 02:04:24,708
当我告诉她只剩几个月的时候
When I told her it was a matter of months,she said,

2012
02:04:24,708 --> 02:04:27,732
她说  "不  医生  不用那么久"
“Oh.no. Doctor,not that long.”

2013
02:04:30,652 --> 02:04:33,884
很好  你已经告诉我们所有我们想知道的事了
You’ve been very kind. You’ve told us all we wanted to know.

2014
02:04:33,989 --> 02:04:36,700
我可能会需要一次正式的审查
We shall need an official verification.

2015
02:04:36,700 --> 02:04:39,828
-审查?  -是的  以确定自杀的裁决
-Verification? -Yes.

2016
02:04:37,887 --> 02:04:40,549
-To confirm the verdict of suicide. -DR.BAKER: I understand.

2017
02:04:39,828 --> 02:04:42,852
我明白  可以请你们喝杯雪利酒吗
Can I offer you gentlemen a glass of sherry?

2018
02:04:42,852 --> 02:04:45,980
不用了  太客气了  我想我们该走了
COLONEL JULYAN: No,that's very kind? I think we ought to be going.

2019
02:04:48,795 --> 02:04:50,776
谢天谢地我们终于知道真相了
Thank heaven we know the truth.

2020
02:04:50,776 --> 02:04:52,757
可怕的事  太可怕了
Dreadfnl thing. Dreadful.

2021
02:04:52,757 --> 02:04:55,573
像她这样一位年轻貌美的女人  难怪
Young and lovely woman like that. No wonder...

2022
02:04:55,573 --> 02:05:00,161
我一点也不明白  丹尼肯定也是
I never had the remotest idea. Neither did Danny,I’m sure.

2023
02:05:01,620 --> 02:05:03,602
希望我是喝醉酒了
I wish I had a drink.

2024
02:05:03,706 --> 02:05:06,208
我们还需要再做进一步审讯吗  朱利安上校
Will we be needed at the inquest any further,Colonel Julyan?

2025
02:05:06,313 --> 02:05:08,919
不用了  我看得出迈克西姆也不想再被骚扰了
No,no.I can see to it that Maxim’s not troubled any further.

2026
02:05:08,919 --> 02:05:11,213
-谢谢  长官  -准备走了吗  上校
-Thank you,sir. -You ready to start,Colonel?

2027
02:05:11,213 --> 02:05:13,820
不用  谢谢  今晚我要待在城里
No,thank you. I’m staying in town tonight.

2028
02:05:13,820 --> 02:05:17,678
费弗尔  敲诈勒索可不是什么好行当
And let me tell you,Favell,blackmail in not much of a profession.

2029
02:05:17,678 --> 02:05:19,816
我们这一带的人知道该怎么对付讹诈
And we know how to deal with it in our part of the world,

2030
02:05:20,170 --> 02:05:21,432
尽管在你看来这或许有点新鲜
strange as it may seem to you.

2031
02:05:21,432 --> 02:05:23,934
我的确不知道你在讲什么
I’m sure I don’t know what you’re talking about.

2032
02:05:24,039 --> 02:05:27,062
上校  但是如果你什么时候需要买车的话就告诉我
But if you ever need a new car,Colonel,just let me know.

2033
02:05:27,062 --> 02:05:30,086
不知该如何感谢你帮忙我们解决了这件事
It’s impossible to thank you for your kindness to us through all this.

2034
02:05:30,086 --> 02:05:31,609
千言万语尽在不言中
You know what I feel without my saying it.

2035
02:05:31,609 --> 02:05:32,797
别客气  别说感谢的话了
Not at all. Put the whole thing behind you.

2036
02:05:32,902 --> 02:05:35,821
最好先通知你太太  她会担心的
But let your wife know. She'll be getting worried.

2037
02:05:35,821 --> 02:05:38,845
是  我会马上打电话给她  然后就直接回曼陀丽
Yes,of course. I’ll phone her at once

2038
02:05:36,362 --> 02:05:37,772
and we’ll get straight down to Manderley.

2039
02:05:38,845 --> 02:05:42,077
再见  克劳莱  迈克西姆是个很好的朋友
Goodbye,Crawley Maxim’s got a great friend.

2040
02:05:48,125 --> 02:05:50,523
-弗兰克  -什么事  迈克西姆
-Frank. -Yes,Maxim?

2041
02:05:52,505 --> 02:05:54,903
有些事你不知道
-There’s something you don’t know. -Oh,no,there isn’t.

2042
02:05:55,007 --> 02:05:57,614
不  我都知道

2043
02:06:05,956 --> 02:06:08,249
我没有杀她  弗兰克
I didn’t kill her, Frank.

2044
02:06:08,249 --> 02:06:10,231
但我现在明白当她告诉我孩子的事时
But I know now that when she told me about the child,

2045
02:06:10,231 --> 02:06:12,525
她想要我杀了她
she wanted me to kill her.

2046
02:06:12,525 --> 02:06:15,653
她故意撒谎  她早已预料到整件事
She lied on purpose. She foresaw the whole thing.

2047
02:06:15,757 --> 02:06:18,572
所以当她 她站在那儿笑
That’s why she stood there laughing when she...

2048
02:06:18,572 --> 02:06:21,179
别再想了
Don’t think about it anymore.

2049
02:06:23,264 --> 02:06:25,350
谢谢你  弗兰克
Thank you,Frank.

2050
02:06:27,123 --> 02:06:30,772
喂  丹尼  我只是想要告诉你个消息
Hello,Danny.I just wanted to tell you the news.

2051
02:06:30,772 --> 02:06:34,943
丽贝卡把我们俩都耍了  她得了癌症
Rebecca held out on both of us. She had cancer.

2052
02:06:36,715 --> 02:06:39,009
是的  是自杀
Yes,suicide.

2053
02:06:39,009 --> 02:06:42,033
从此以后迈克斯跟他亲爱的小新娘
Now Max and that dear little bride of his

2054
02:06:42,033 --> 02:06:45,891
将会继续幸福地在曼陀丽生活
will be able to stay on at Manderley and live happily ever after.

2055
02:06:47,247 --> 02:06:49,228
再见  丹尼
Bye-bye,Danny.

2056
02:06:52,148 --> 02:06:55,484
-这是你的车吗  先生  -是的
-This your car,sir? -Yes.

2057
02:06:55,484 --> 02:06:58,508
可以马上开走吗  这不是停车位
Will you be going soon? This isn’t a parking place,you know.

2058
02:06:58,508 --> 02:07:00,489
不是吗  如果想的话
Oh,isn’t it? Well,people are entitled to leave cars outside if they want to.

2059
02:07:00,489 --> 02:07:02,679
我就有权把车停在外面

2060
02:07:02,679 --> 02:07:06,224
真遗憾  你们这些家伙没什么好事可做的
It’s a pity some of you fellows haven’t anything to do.

2061
02:07:09,457 --> 02:07:12,480
你打电话回去的时候  她说会等你回来吗
When you phoned,did she say she’d wait up?

2062
02:07:12,480 --> 02:07:15,609
我让她先睡  可她不听
I asked her to go to bed,but she wouldn't hear of it.

2063
02:07:17,173 --> 02:07:20,196
真希望能开得再快点儿
I wish I could get some more speed out of this thing.

2064
02:07:20,196 --> 02:07:22,699
你在担心什么  迈克西姆
Is something worrying you,Maxim?

2065
02:07:22,699 --> 02:07:25,723
事情有点不对头  有点不妙
I can’t get over the feeling something’s wrong.

2066
02:08:13,270 --> 02:08:15,669
-弗兰克  -怎么了  干吗停车
-Frank. -What’s the matter? Why did we stop?

2067
02:08:15,773 --> 02:08:17,754
现在几点了
What’s the time?

2068
02:08:17,754 --> 02:08:20,674
这表不准  肯定是3、4点了  怎么了
Well,this clock’s wrong. It must be 3:00 or 4:00. Why?

2069
02:08:20,674 --> 02:08:22,968
那不可能是破晓黎明
That can’t be the dawn breaking over there.

2070
02:08:22,968 --> 02:08:25,679
因为是冬天  所以你看到北极光了吧
It’s in the winter that you see the northern Iights,isn’t it?

2071
02:08:27,555 --> 02:08:30,788
那不是北极光  那是曼陀丽
That’s not the northern lights. That’s Manderley.

2072
02:08:53,727 --> 02:08:56,751
弗里思  弗里思  德温特太太呢  她在哪儿
Frith! Frith!

2073
02:08:55,019 --> 02:08:56,304
Mrs.de Winter. Where is she?

2074
02:08:56,751 --> 02:08:58,941
-我想我看到过她  先生  -在哪儿
-I thought I saw her,sir -Where?

2075
02:09:06,136 --> 02:09:07,595
迈克西姆
Maxim!

2076
02:09:09,368 --> 02:09:13,820
-谢天谢地你回来了  -你没事吧  快告诉我
Thank heavens you’ve come back to me!

2077
02:09:11,118 --> 02:09:12,699
-Are you all right,darling? -Oh,yes,I am.

2078
02:09:13,820 --> 02:09:14,894
-没事  我没事  -你没事吧
Are you all right?

2079
02:09:14,894 --> 02:09:17,710
是丹弗斯太太放的火  她疯了
Mrs.Danvers,she’s gone mad.

2080
02:09:17,710 --> 02:09:19,086
她说宁愿毁掉曼陀丽
She said she’d rather destroy Manderley than see us happy here.

2081
02:09:19,086 --> 02:09:20,838
也不要看着我们幸福地住在这儿

2082
02:09:20,942 --> 02:09:24,279
看  快看西厢
